âœ… how to install and run firefox inside docker

steps-

1..Build Docker Image from dockerfile

2.build the image
docker build -t firefox-image .


3.linux host with X11
docker run -it \
    --rm \
    -e DISPLAY=$DISPLAY \
    -v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix \
    --device /dev/snd \
    --name firefox-runner \
    firefox-image

4.revoke X11 access
xhost -local:root

    


